"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-callum-dixon-paris-olympics-2024-rowing-dyslexia-b1173073.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport  As an energetic eight-year-old, the thought first popped into Callum Dixon's head: \\\"When am I going to learn to read?\\\"\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Dixon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Callum Dixon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Dixon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Callum_Dixon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His friends had begun to master it but, for him, the words would not stick together.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He would not lose track of the letters, nor would they float around the page but he could not differentiate a b from a d, a p from a q and an m from a w.  It is a predicament he still faces nearly two decades on in the build-up to theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had that expectation that one day it would just click but I suddenly realised that wasn't going to happen,\\\" he recalled.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not long after that, he was diagnosed with dyslexia.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even in adult life, reading a book or even a menu is beyond him, and he can only read a few words at a time on a page.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Born and brought up in Mile End, he estimates he spent three weeks in school before being pulled out - his mum suggests it was closer to three days - and he was homeschooled after that.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As I grew up, every year or so there was re-evaluation do we think school is a good idea?\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember quite early on that I could either be normal in a special school for want of a better word, or be special in a normal school and neither one of those options appealed in any way.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nottingham Forest vs Arsenal: Premier League - LIVE  Egypt vs Nigeria LIVE: Latest score and updates from AFCON third-place play-off  Chelsea vs Brentford LIVE: Latest score and updates from Premier League  Little masterpieces: The ING Discerning Eye exhibition returns  \\\"With the homeschooling, I am sure there were days which probably ended with us all yelling [he was homeschooled with his brother and sister] but those are not the days I remember.\\\"\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1592, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.20544785055503e-12, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1649, \"end\": 1663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3454820487100826e-18, \"text\": \"Premier League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ones he remembers are learning about London as a Roman city on a BBC documentary and visiting walls in the flesh that still stood from that era the following day.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1953, \"end\": 1959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999961737558, \"rank\": 3.5987067489884512e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1965, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Rome\", \"score\": 0.9458275262362063, \"rank\": 0.0497794183182239, \"text\": \"Roman\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Rome\"}, {\"begin\": 1981, \"end\": 1984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9990026544223696, \"rank\": 0.0009569866903025069, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, it's all positive memories,\\\" he added, \\\"helped by the fact my mum had the patience of a saint.\\\"\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To get both exercise and socialisation, he was thrown into every after-school club imaginable London and that was where he relished.\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He looked to have found his slot with sailing and was part of the finn set-up within British Sailing set to take over from the likes ofBen Ainslieand Giles Scott before the class was scrapped from the Olympic programme.\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2385, \"end\": 2389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finn_the_Human\", \"score\": 0.9998995728028608, \"rank\": 0.00010043680547736623, \"text\": \"finn\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finn_the_Human\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finn_the_Human\"}, {\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9612390096631029, \"rank\": 0.036657597701818576, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2469, \"end\": 2480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giles_Scott\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giles Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giles_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giles_Scott\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having relocated to Portland in Dorset as part of the squad, he needed another re-evaluation.\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2560, \"end\": 2568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Portland\", \"score\": 0.9887948849665408, \"rank\": 0.01099136338798, \"text\": \"Portland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Portland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Portland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was a shock which we did not see coming,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was pretty heartbreaking.\\\"\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, he moved back home and instead tried out his hand at rowing.\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His first time in a boat was at the end of September 2019, that day he remembers falling in 17 times.\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For much of the next few months, he kept on falling in before Covid struck and his foray into a new sport was put on hold.\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He had the fitness and physical attributes needed to crack the sport just not the technical skills.\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember thinking if I learn to row I might be ok,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All I needed to do was learn how to row.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That became more manageable when I stopped falling in.\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd already ticked most of the boxes naturally to be a rower: right size, right weight, right background.\\\"\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His climb has been rapid, selected in the quadruple sculls where Britain is one of four realistic contenders for an Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3448, \"end\": 3455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9976873323522444, \"rank\": 0.0023179926300599786, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is also a livelihood where his dyslexia is not a feature.\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He knows what will not always be the case and, while he does not have sleepless nights thinking about it, the dyslexia does \\\"affect how I think about the future.\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sure that will present challenges\\\".\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has overcome many challenges, notably gaining a psychology degree from the Open University, an achievement arguably more impressive than becoming an Olympian.\", \"from\": 3780, \"to\": 3941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3858, \"end\": 3873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Open_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.4018901244650046e-18, \"text\": \"Open University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Open_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Open_University\"}, {\"begin\": 3932, \"end\": 3940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999677129, \"rank\": 2.0472035482705537e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am proud of my rowing achievement but I had all the right opportunities,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 4028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whereas with the university degree, there were a lot more things saying, 'no way'.\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had no other education certificate, I can not read a single word basically.\", \"from\": 4113, \"to\": 4190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There were lots of things that said it probably would not work.\\\"\", \"from\": 4191, \"to\": 4255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 4257, \"to\": 5135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4317, \"end\": 4326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9984180512193812, \"rank\": 0.0015835584415301676, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 4417, \"end\": 4426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9984180512193812, \"rank\": 0.0015835584415301676, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 4495, \"end\": 4503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\", \"score\": 0.9999999999727152, \"rank\": 2.7040094305860107e-11, \"text\": \"Brighton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\"}, {\"begin\": 4561, \"end\": 4575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3454820487100826e-18, \"text\": \"Premier League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\"}, {\"begin\": 4599, \"end\": 4607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\", \"score\": 0.9999999999727152, \"rank\": 2.7